---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="ApopTosis AI — STEM + LANG = SAFE">
  <section class="hero bg-gradient-to-b from-prime-blue to-black min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="flux-ring absolute inset-0 m-auto w-96 h-96 opacity-30 animate-pulse">
      <div class="stem">STEM</div>
      <div class="safe">SAFE</div>
      <div class="lang">LANG</div>
      <div class="center-symbol">π</div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center z-10 px-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-garamond text-prime-gold mb-8 leading-tight">
        Not to win.<br>To cooperate.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-3xl mb-8 font-bold">STEM + LANG = SAFE</p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8 text-lg">
        <div>
          <p class="text-prime-gold mb-2">STEM (Expansion)</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
            <li>Science: Governance → Equality</li>
            <li>Mathematics: Arts → Freedom</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-prime-gold mb-2">LANG (Contraction)</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
            <li>Norms: Tech → Security</li>
            <li>Engineering: Logic → Accountability</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-4">
        1/2 human perspective + 1/2 reversible intelligence = a future that is secure, accountable, free, and equal — by mathematical law.
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4 mt-8">
        <a href="/ethics" class="bg-prime-gold text-prime-blue px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-opacity-80">Explore Ethics</a>
        <a href="/primeflux" class="border-2 border-prime-gold text-prime-gold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-prime-gold hover:text-prime-blue">PrimeFlux Math</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
